-- MGM, Kerzner plan new Las Vegas resort
-- 
-- Wed Jun 20, 2007 8:28am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/06/20/us-mgm-kerzner-idUSN2021675120070620

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - MGM Mirage Inc. ( MGM.N ) and resort developer Kerzner International Holdings Ltd. on Wednesday said they plan to enter a joint venture to develop a multibillion-dollar resort on the Las Vegas Strip. 

 MGM plans to provide the land for the resort, while Kerzner and its parents will provide financing for the 50-50 joint venture.